example.code:
Cloudflare config (broken):
  SSL/TLS mode = Flexible

Origin nginx (also broken in combination):
  server {
    listen 80;
    return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
  }
  server {
    listen 443 ssl;
    ...
  }

Result for browser hitting https://example.com:
  1. Browser → Cloudflare (HTTPS terminated at edge)
  2. Cloudflare → origin port 80 (Flexible mode = HTTP)
  3. nginx 301 → https://example.com
  4. Browser → Cloudflare → origin port 80 → 301 → ...
  ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS after ~10-20 hops.

Fix: switch SSL to Full (Strict), install origin cert, never Flexible.
